%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to see"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to see"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make (someone) see","tags":["ditransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَصِرَ (baṣira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vision, sight, gaze","examples":[{"text":"إِذْ جَاؤُوكُمْ مِنْ فَوْقِكُمْ وَمِنْ أَسْفَلَ مِنْكُمْ وَإِذْ زَاغَتْ الأَبْصَارُ وَبَلَغَتْ الْقُلُوبُ الْحَنَاجِرَ وَتَظُنُّونَ بِاللّٰهِ الظُّنُونَا","english":"[Remember] when they came at you from above you and from below you, and when the gazes shifted, and the hearts reached the throats and you assumed about Allah assumptions."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2635","headword_ar":"بَصُرَ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (Sb, M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSira","text_ar":"بَصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (Lh, K, ) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biSaArapN","text_ar":"بِصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He saw;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became seeing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra muboSirFA","text_ar":"صَارَ مُبْصِرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Sb, M, K;) with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to the noun following. (K.) But see 4, in four places."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSura","text_ar":"بَصُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is seldom used to signify the sense of sight unless to this meaning is conjoined that of mental perception. (B.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSura","text_ar":"بَصُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSira","text_ar":"بَصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, endowed with mental perception;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm belief;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge, understanding, intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurabihi","text_ar":"بَصُرَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S Msb, B,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSirabihi","text_ar":"بَصِرَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurahu","text_ar":"بَصُرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSirahu","text_ar":"بَصِرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but more chastely with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and *"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbSrhu","text_ar":"ابصرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He perceived it mentally;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he knew it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understood it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurotu bimaA lamo yaboSuruwA bihi","text_ar":"بَصُرْتُ بِمَا لَمْ يَبْصُرُوا بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xx. 96], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I knew that which they knew not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSara AlA^adiymayoni","text_ar":"بَصَرَ الاَدِيمَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSorN","text_ar":"بَصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the two hides together, and sewed them, like as the two edges of a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, are sewed, one being put upon the other; which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode of sewing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is contrary to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"different from, that in which a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, is sewed before it is sewed the second time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put together the two edges of the two hides, when they were being sewed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, is sewed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["Sb","M","K","Lh","T","S"]}]}}